{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The rate of detections\/recognitions per second in energy save mode."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Defaults to 1, meaning that 1 frame per second is detected\/recognized."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"When the video frame rate is 30, 29 frames will be skipped, 1 frame is detected\/recognized."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Note: if you set the detection rate greater to or equal to the video frame rate, no frames will be skipped,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the actual detection rate is limited by the video frame rate."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Note: Usually you set a much lower value here as for the detectionRate property to save energy."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/energySaveDetectionRate"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/energysavedetectionrate"]},{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/energysavedetectionrate"]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"dynamic"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"energySaveDetectionRate"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Su","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UInt"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"set"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"]]},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"energySaveDetectionRate","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UInt","preciseIdentifier":"s:Su","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","modules":[{"name":"ScanbotSDK"}],"title":"energySaveDetectionRate","externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration(py)energySaveDetectionRate","symbolKind":"property","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"energySaveDetectionRate"}]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://net.doo.ScanbotSDK/documentation/ScanbotSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration/energySaveDetectionRate":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"energySaveDetectionRate"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The rate of detections\/recognitions per second in energy save mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Defaults to 1, meaning that 1 frame per second is detected\/recognized.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"When the video frame rate is 30, 29 frames will be skipped, 1 frame is detected\/recognized.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Note: if you set the detection rate greater to or equal to the video frame rate, no frames will be skipped,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the actual detection rate is limited by the video frame rate."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Note: Usually you set a much lower value here as for the detectionRate property to save energy."}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/energysavedetectionrate","title":"energySaveDetectionRate","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/energySaveDetectionRate","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"energySaveDetectionRate"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Su","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UInt"}]},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotSDK/documentation/ScanbotSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The energy management configuration object for a ‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and its subclasses."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and subclasses sport a customizable energy management system."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Since scanners running on a live video feed can put a lot of load onto the CPU and\/or GPU"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the device, causing the battery to drain quickly and running the device hot, you can customize the energy"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"consumption using this class by configuring the rate of detections\/recognitions per second in performance mode as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"well as in energy saving mode."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In performance mode the scanners will be fed with a higher, configurable rate of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"video frames per second.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"After a certain, configurable period of inactivity the energy save mode will be engaged and the rate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of scans will be reduced to a lower (configurable) rate.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You can also configure the time of inactivity before the automatic mode switches from performance to energy save mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Inactivity here means that both of the following conditions are met:","type":"text"}],"title":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}]},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotSDK/documentation/ScanbotSDK":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK","abstract":[{"text":"Version: 8.0.1","type":"text"}],"title":"ScanbotSDK","type":"topic","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk","kind":"symbol"}},"variantOverrides":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"patch":[{"value":"occ","op":"replace","path":"\/identifier\/interfaceLanguage"},{"path":"\/metadata\/roleHeading","value":"Instance Property","op":"replace"},{"path":"\/metadata\/title","value":"energySaveDetectionRate","op":"replace"},{"path":"\/metadata\/symbolKind","value":"property","op":"replace"},{"path":"\/metadata\/fragments","value":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"energySaveDetectionRate"}],"op":"replace"},{"path":"\/topicSections","value":null,"op":"add"},{"path":"\/relationshipsSections","value":null,"op":"add"},{"path":"\/seeAlsoSections","value":null,"op":"add"},{"path":"\/primaryContentSections\/0","value":{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSUInteger","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSUInteger"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"energySaveDetectionRate"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},"op":"replace"},{"path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotSDK~1SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration~1energySaveDetectionRate\/title","value":"energySaveDetectionRate","op"